1
00:00:29,399 --> 00:00:31,039
(The heart-fluttering first date begins.)

2
00:00:31,239 --> 00:00:32,439
Will you do me all the favors?

3
00:00:33,109 --> 00:00:35,239
(If you ask, I will.)

4
00:00:35,309 --> 00:00:37,109
(Proactive expressions)

5
00:00:37,909 --> 00:00:40,219
(Their feelings grow stronger.)

6
00:00:41,179 --> 00:00:44,319
(They're excited about the unusual atmosphere.)

7
00:00:44,949 --> 00:00:47,719
(Si Woo wrote a letter to Hee Dong before the date.)

8
00:00:52,759 --> 00:00:54,829
(However, Hee Dong couldn't read it.)

9
00:00:55,229 --> 00:00:56,229
Shall I help you?

10
00:00:56,669 --> 00:00:59,639
(He and Seo Yoon have grown closer.)

11
00:01:00,469 --> 00:01:04,639
(And Si Woo is waiting for him.)

12
00:01:05,369 --> 00:01:06,538
She's bothered by her.

13
00:01:06,539 --> 00:01:08,279
Si Woo is extremely bothered by Seo Yoon.

14
00:01:08,309 --> 00:01:09,539
Hi.

15
00:01:11,279 --> 00:01:15,049
(The atmosphere has changed completely as Seo Yoon joins.)

16
00:01:15,219 --> 00:01:16,278
Did you go to a workshop?

17
00:01:16,279 --> 00:01:17,489
We made it.

18
00:01:18,119 --> 00:01:22,719
(Si Woo could do nothing but listen to the two's date.)

19
00:01:23,229 --> 00:01:24,789
The two grew close.

20
00:01:25,759 --> 00:01:31,498
(What will happen to the three?)

21
00:01:31,499 --> 00:01:36,439
(Episode 4: A New Start)

22
00:01:37,909 --> 00:01:39,639
It's the evening of the second day.

23
00:01:40,179 --> 00:01:42,939
We can't even grasp how the days will unfold from now on.

24
00:01:45,149 --> 00:01:46,278
You must be hungry.

25
00:01:46,279 --> 00:01:47,579
Should we start right away?

26
00:01:47,919 --> 00:01:48,948
Let's go.

27
00:01:48,949 --> 00:01:50,709
(Preparing dinner for Seo Yoon and Hee Dong)

28
00:01:50,819 --> 00:01:53,059
Please put this back in the fridge.

29
00:01:53,419 --> 00:01:54,919
Is it too much? It is, right?

30
00:01:55,319 --> 00:01:56,688
A little less?

31
00:01:56,689 --> 00:01:57,935
- It's okay.
- You like kimchi, right?

32
00:01:57,959 --> 00:01:59,028
- A housewarming party?
- Doesn't it look like...

33
00:01:59,029 --> 00:02:00,029
they are having a get-together?

34
00:02:00,030 --> 00:02:02,470
(They're watching like they've come to a housewarming party.)

35
00:02:04,429 --> 00:02:06,439
Why didn't you use warm water?

36
00:02:07,599 --> 00:02:09,908
If you're cold, go and put something on.

37
00:02:09,909 --> 00:02:11,069
- Can I?
- Yes.

38
00:02:11,869 --> 00:02:13,578
But what I have isn't for cooking.

39
00:02:13,579 --> 00:02:14,839
I don't have anything to wear.

40
00:02:15,009 --> 00:02:16,779
- Should I lend you mine?
- The coat?

41
00:02:17,949 --> 00:02:20,379
- The one from earlier?
- Okay.

42
00:02:20,979 --> 00:02:21,979
Okay.

43
00:02:28,089 --> 00:02:29,089
This will look cool.

44
00:02:29,090 --> 00:02:30,130
(He brings out something.)

45
00:02:31,489 --> 00:02:32,489
Here.

46
00:02:32,889 --> 00:02:34,289
Wear this and cook like a pro chef.

47
00:02:34,529 --> 00:02:35,959
Thank you. Let me wash my hands.

48
00:02:38,429 --> 00:02:43,369
(He has brought a leather jacket when she's cooking.)

49
00:02:45,639 --> 00:02:47,139
- I might get it dirty.
- It's black.

50
00:02:47,679 --> 00:02:49,208
It's leather, so you can wipe it off right away.

51
00:02:49,209 --> 00:02:50,248
(She tries it on in front of everyone.)

52
00:02:50,249 --> 00:02:51,309
Thank you.

53
00:02:51,849 --> 00:02:53,548
Cooking with this on is...

54
00:02:53,549 --> 00:02:54,549
(Embarrassed)

55
00:02:56,279 --> 00:02:57,549
I'm expecting a fire show now.

56
00:03:00,389 --> 00:03:04,489
I'm really not sure if I can wear this to make kimchi fried rice.

57
00:03:04,529 --> 00:03:07,059
(The sleeves are getting in the way.)

58
00:03:07,799 --> 00:03:10,929
You should pull the sleeves up for her.

59
00:03:15,099 --> 00:03:17,439
(Going on his knees)

60
00:03:18,039 --> 00:03:19,838
- This much?
- That'll do.

61
00:03:19,839 --> 00:03:21,109
- Are you sure?
- Yes.

62
00:03:22,079 --> 00:03:23,079
What?

63
00:03:23,479 --> 00:03:24,979
He kneeled.

64
00:03:25,079 --> 00:03:27,719
- Yoon Hoo is cool.
- How sweet of him.

65
00:03:28,019 --> 00:03:29,819
Did he have to go that far?

66
00:03:29,849 --> 00:03:31,689
I know, right? Isn't that a little too much?

67
00:03:31,949 --> 00:03:34,858
That's the bare minimum.

68
00:03:34,859 --> 00:03:36,289
See his perfect posture?

69
00:03:37,559 --> 00:03:39,558
I'm jealous of Yu Bin.

70
00:03:39,559 --> 00:03:40,559
(Feeling proud)

71
00:03:41,659 --> 00:03:43,468
- This much?
- That'll do.

72
00:03:43,469 --> 00:03:44,669
- Are you sure?
- Yes.

73
00:03:45,699 --> 00:03:46,739
Thank you.

74
00:03:49,969 --> 00:03:53,008
(Thanks to the two chefs on good terms, )

75
00:03:53,009 --> 00:03:56,709
(the late-night snack is cooking nicely.)

76
00:03:58,979 --> 00:03:59,979
Dig in.

77
00:04:00,049 --> 00:04:01,548
(Dinner by Yu Bin and Yoon Hoo is done.)

78
00:04:01,549 --> 00:04:02,979
Thank you.

79
00:04:07,059 --> 00:04:08,059
Have the first bite.

80
00:04:08,419 --> 00:04:09,459
Okay.

81
00:04:09,889 --> 00:04:13,858
(Seo Yoon and Hee Dong eat dinner sitting across from each other.)

82
00:04:13,859 --> 00:04:14,859
It's good.

83
00:04:14,860 --> 00:04:16,199
- Is it? I'm glad.
- Yes.

84
00:04:19,699 --> 00:04:21,199
Those two are having dinner alone.

85
00:04:21,869 --> 00:04:22,869
They look good together.

86
00:04:25,539 --> 00:04:26,809
(Glancing)

87
00:04:27,539 --> 00:04:30,008
I want to sit down, but I just can't because it's too cold.

88
00:04:30,009 --> 00:04:31,079
Sit on this side.

89
00:04:32,049 --> 00:04:33,518
That side is really cold.

90
00:04:33,519 --> 00:04:34,519
- Sit on the inside.
- Okay.

91
00:04:34,520 --> 00:04:37,549
(Taking a seat)

92
00:04:43,159 --> 00:04:44,358
She sat next to him.

93
00:04:44,359 --> 00:04:45,359
- Next to him.
- She keeps sitting...

94
00:04:45,359 --> 00:04:46,359
- next to Hee Dong.
- Right?

95
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:47,600
(Si Woo sits next to Hee Dong.)

96
00:04:52,469 --> 00:04:54,198
Isn't the vibe nice here?

97
00:04:54,199 --> 00:04:55,299
- It is.
- Right?

98
00:04:55,939 --> 00:04:57,538
Everyone is so kind.

99
00:04:57,539 --> 00:04:59,839
- Sorry?
- Everyone is so kind.

100
00:05:06,309 --> 00:05:08,619
It was tough in the cold, wasn't it?

101
00:05:09,649 --> 00:05:12,719
Didn't you say you went to the beach?

102
00:05:13,219 --> 00:05:15,558
No, we had a meal and went to a doll workshop.

103
00:05:15,559 --> 00:05:17,129
Right, you said you made the dolls.

104
00:05:26,469 --> 00:05:29,039
You look greedy, using both hands.

105
00:05:29,569 --> 00:05:30,909
I'm ambidextrous.

106
00:05:31,269 --> 00:05:32,369
Is that so?

107
00:05:35,879 --> 00:05:40,249
(The conversation continues without Si Woo.)

108
00:05:41,779 --> 00:05:43,179
Nobody is talking to Si Woo.

109
00:05:44,119 --> 00:05:45,489
Say something, Si Woo.

110
00:05:48,559 --> 00:05:52,029
I barely talked to Hee Dong,

111
00:05:52,959 --> 00:05:54,658
but she spent the whole day with him.

112
00:05:54,659 --> 00:05:58,169
I'm sure they've talked a lot.

113
00:05:58,829 --> 00:06:00,969
It was a bummer.

114
00:06:08,109 --> 00:06:09,948
(In the end, Si Woo leaves the two.)

115
00:06:09,949 --> 00:06:11,179
Do you need a hand?

116
00:06:13,209 --> 00:06:14,848
Nobody is talking to Si Woo.

117
00:06:14,849 --> 00:06:16,379
The conversation didn't continue.

118
00:06:16,479 --> 00:06:18,418
Even though she sat down to chat.

119
00:06:18,419 --> 00:06:20,379
(There's a distance between Si Woo and Hee Dong.)

120
00:06:31,629 --> 00:06:32,998
- Are you done?
- What?

121
00:06:32,999 --> 00:06:34,769
- Are you done eating?
- Yes.

122
00:06:35,069 --> 00:06:36,569
- Should we clean up?
- Okay.

123
00:06:40,009 --> 00:06:41,279
They must be done.

124
00:06:53,089 --> 00:06:57,559
(Si Woo can't leave Hee Dong, who's doing the dishes.)

125
00:07:00,299 --> 00:07:02,458
I bet Si Woo wants to ask if he read the letter.

126
00:07:02,459 --> 00:07:04,169
- She must be dying to ask.
- Totally.

127
00:07:09,039 --> 00:07:12,609
(Si Woo hangs around the kitchen, )

128
00:07:13,409 --> 00:07:18,009
(but Hee Dong doesn't turn back.)

129
00:07:21,179 --> 00:07:23,079
- I'm leaving first.
- Okay.

130
00:07:25,189 --> 00:07:26,388
She gave up.

131
00:07:26,389 --> 00:07:30,029
Si Woo ends up leaving first.

132
00:07:35,599 --> 00:07:36,728
For real.

133
00:07:36,729 --> 00:07:38,199
(Glancing)

134
00:07:38,969 --> 00:07:39,969
Got it.

135
00:07:39,970 --> 00:07:42,899
(Glancing)

136
00:07:43,099 --> 00:07:45,239
It's best if I do it since I'm already at it.

137
00:07:48,579 --> 00:07:53,819
(Si Woo can't help but keep looking toward the kitchen.)

138
00:07:56,819 --> 00:07:58,989
(Glancing)

139
00:08:01,919 --> 00:08:04,089
(Glancing)

140
00:08:05,329 --> 00:08:07,399
His date was with Eun Byul,

141
00:08:07,799 --> 00:08:10,128
but his initial interest was in Si Woo.

142
00:08:10,129 --> 00:08:11,199
Correct.

143
00:08:13,739 --> 00:08:14,999
Can I light it up?

144
00:08:16,039 --> 00:08:18,169
- Would you like to try?
- Yes.

145
00:08:23,709 --> 00:08:25,379
(Flinching)

146
00:08:27,919 --> 00:08:30,289
(Getting up)

147
00:08:34,859 --> 00:08:36,989
(Glancing)

148
00:08:37,089 --> 00:08:38,089
One more time.

149
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:39,559
How?

150
00:08:39,560 --> 00:08:41,920
(Eun Byul is conscious of Jae Hyuk, who is helping Si Woo.)

151
00:08:46,629 --> 00:08:47,838
Eun Byul is...

152
00:08:47,839 --> 00:08:50,168
- Eun Byul is watching the two.
- She is.

153
00:08:50,169 --> 00:08:51,409
Eun Byul totally is.

154
00:08:51,869 --> 00:08:53,439
What's up with Jae Hyuk?

155
00:08:53,539 --> 00:08:55,038
What's up with Jae Hyuk, Tae Yong?

156
00:08:55,039 --> 00:08:58,878
Jae Hyuk got close to Eon Byul all naturally.

157
00:08:58,879 --> 00:09:00,118
It's Eun Byul, not Eon Byul.

158
00:09:00,119 --> 00:09:01,419
Right, Eun Byul.

159
00:09:01,479 --> 00:09:04,489
I'm sorry, my pronunciation is bad.

160
00:09:04,849 --> 00:09:06,349
- Eun Byul.
- Eon Byul.

161
00:09:08,389 --> 00:09:09,958
- So?
- So his interest...

162
00:09:09,959 --> 00:09:11,559
- in Eun Byul has grown a lot, - But?

163
00:09:11,789 --> 00:09:13,758
But he's also still interested in Si Woo.

164
00:09:13,759 --> 00:09:14,898
- Still, right?
- Basically,

165
00:09:14,899 --> 00:09:16,059
Jae Hyuk is reading the room.

166
00:09:16,899 --> 00:09:18,928
- To be honest, yes?
- Yes.

167
00:09:18,929 --> 00:09:21,068
A man doesn't change his mind so quickly.

168
00:09:21,069 --> 00:09:22,589
- He's still interested in her.
- Yes.

169
00:09:24,469 --> 00:09:25,608
(The evening after their first date)

170
00:09:25,609 --> 00:09:27,579
It's best if I do it since I'm already at it.

171
00:09:30,179 --> 00:09:32,948
(Their feelings for each other...)

172
00:09:32,949 --> 00:09:37,819
(are getting tangled up.)

173
00:09:39,689 --> 00:09:41,159
- Let's go.
- I appreciate it.

174
00:09:43,689 --> 00:09:45,958
(With complicated feelings, all the children have gathered.)

175
00:09:45,959 --> 00:09:48,759
It'd be nice if they got a chance to talk.

176
00:09:52,029 --> 00:09:53,099
It's here.

177
00:09:53,499 --> 00:09:54,599
Finally.

178
00:09:59,639 --> 00:10:01,408
(The 1-on-1 Rotation Chat starts now.)

179
00:10:01,409 --> 00:10:02,409
"Rotation Chat?"

180
00:10:02,410 --> 00:10:04,408
- It's a 1-on-1 Rotation Chat.
- "The 1-on-1 Rotation Chat starts."

181
00:10:04,409 --> 00:10:10,319
(The 1-on-1 Rotation Chat starts now.)

182
00:10:11,989 --> 00:10:13,119
Right away?

183
00:10:15,759 --> 00:10:17,859
The 1-on-1 Rotation Chat goes like this.

184
00:10:17,989 --> 00:10:20,429
The boys wait at their designated spots.

185
00:10:20,929 --> 00:10:23,499
- The girls go around in turns.
- Okay.

186
00:10:23,729 --> 00:10:25,298
The 1-on-1 Rotation Chat lasts...

187
00:10:25,299 --> 00:10:26,628
- for 10 minutes.
- For 10 minutes.

188
00:10:26,629 --> 00:10:28,975
(It's short, but a chance to talk to everyone of the opposite sex.)

189
00:10:28,999 --> 00:10:30,438
- That's short.
- They get ten minutes,

190
00:10:30,439 --> 00:10:32,869
so it's their golden chance to chat with the person...

191
00:10:32,939 --> 00:10:34,538
they've been wanting to talk to.

192
00:10:34,539 --> 00:10:35,878
Exactly, it's their chance.

193
00:10:35,879 --> 00:10:38,208
- That's right, Si Woo.
- Don't miss it, Si Woo.

194
00:10:38,209 --> 00:10:40,109
Yes. It's a chance for everyone.

195
00:10:40,949 --> 00:10:45,419
Honestly, the 1-on-1 chat is a rare opportunity.

196
00:10:45,789 --> 00:10:48,689
"Make good use of it," is what crossed my mind.

197
00:10:49,389 --> 00:10:52,889
It may be short, but it's a good opportunity.

198
00:10:54,899 --> 00:10:56,829
Getting the chance made me happy.

199
00:10:58,629 --> 00:11:01,969
(Guys, please head to your designated spots.)

200
00:11:02,769 --> 00:11:04,509
(1st floor kitchen, Yoon Hoo)

201
00:11:05,469 --> 00:11:07,309
(1st floor hideout, Lee Jae Seung)

202
00:11:08,039 --> 00:11:09,779
(1st floor living room, Shin Jae Hyuk)

203
00:11:10,609 --> 00:11:12,709
(3rd floor letter room, You Hee Dong)

204
00:11:13,479 --> 00:11:16,748
(Who were you excited to talk to?)

205
00:11:16,749 --> 00:11:18,348
I'm not close with anyone,

206
00:11:18,349 --> 00:11:19,949
so I'd love to get to know all of them.

207
00:11:20,719 --> 00:11:24,759
I want to talk to Eun Byul.

208
00:11:25,159 --> 00:11:27,029
I want to chat with Si Woo.

209
00:11:28,359 --> 00:11:30,128
- It's...
- They must be excited about it.

210
00:11:30,129 --> 00:11:32,328
- The feelings must get across.
- I'm so curious.

211
00:11:32,329 --> 00:11:35,339
(What kind of conversations will they have?)

212
00:11:36,239 --> 00:11:40,038
(Who will Hee Dong talk to first?)

213
00:11:40,039 --> 00:11:41,939
- Hi.
- Hi.

214
00:11:45,149 --> 00:11:49,349
(1-on-1 Rotation Chat, You Hee Dong and Choi Yu Bin)

215
00:11:49,919 --> 00:11:51,719
- It's Yu Bin.
- Yu Bin.

216
00:11:52,219 --> 00:11:53,988
Yu Bin received three votes.

217
00:11:53,989 --> 00:11:56,889
(Hee Dong chose Yu Bin during the Attraction Selection.)

218
00:12:02,029 --> 00:12:04,529
- Have you gotten used to things?
- Sort of.

219
00:12:05,469 --> 00:12:08,739
I've settled in well after a night's sleep.

220
00:12:09,699 --> 00:12:11,638
You cook us delicious food every day.

221
00:12:11,639 --> 00:12:13,338
That's really nothing.

222
00:12:13,339 --> 00:12:15,778
The kimchi fried rice you made earlier was good.

223
00:12:15,779 --> 00:12:16,978
- Was it?
- Yes.

224
00:12:16,979 --> 00:12:18,479
Really? I'm relieved.

225
00:12:20,379 --> 00:12:22,579
- I prepared a question...
- Yes?

226
00:12:23,719 --> 00:12:26,619
You wouldn't answer unless it was a time like this.

227
00:12:27,559 --> 00:12:28,559
All right.

228
00:12:28,989 --> 00:12:30,258
(What could be the question?)

229
00:12:30,259 --> 00:12:31,528
She has a question for him?

230
00:12:31,529 --> 00:12:32,758
She must've written it down.

231
00:12:32,759 --> 00:12:34,098
I trust you, Yu Bin.

232
00:12:34,099 --> 00:12:35,829
(Yoon Hoo's dad feels uneasy.)

233
00:12:36,599 --> 00:12:39,669
Here's my question.

234
00:12:40,539 --> 00:12:43,169
Can I ask it so straightforwardly?

235
00:12:43,499 --> 00:12:44,968
- Straightforward is good.
- Really?

236
00:12:44,969 --> 00:12:46,139
- Yes.
- Okay.

237
00:12:48,039 --> 00:12:51,178
I wanted to know who you chose yesterday.

238
00:12:51,179 --> 00:12:53,579
(I want to know who you chose for the Attraction Selection.)

239
00:12:58,589 --> 00:13:01,318
Wouldn't anyone be curious?

240
00:13:01,319 --> 00:13:03,688
I was most attracted...

241
00:13:03,689 --> 00:13:06,389
to Yoon Hoo and Hee Dong.

242
00:13:07,229 --> 00:13:10,199
I asked because I am interested in him.

243
00:13:10,259 --> 00:13:12,499
Appearance-wise,

244
00:13:13,199 --> 00:13:15,239
he's extremely close to my ideal type.

245
00:13:15,769 --> 00:13:19,538
If the text message was really from Hee Dong,

246
00:13:19,539 --> 00:13:22,539
"Why me?" was what I've been wanting to know.

247
00:13:22,809 --> 00:13:25,779
That's why I asked him outright.

248
00:13:28,649 --> 00:13:32,419
(Yu Bin asks the question without hesitation.)

249
00:13:33,989 --> 00:13:35,219
I...

250
00:13:39,159 --> 00:13:41,598
- I sent it to you.
- You did?

251
00:13:41,599 --> 00:13:44,629
(I sent it to you.)

252
00:13:47,999 --> 00:13:48,999
I see.

253
00:13:49,439 --> 00:13:51,039
(Cheering)

254
00:13:51,739 --> 00:13:52,739
(Yu Bin is on cloud nine.)

255
00:13:52,740 --> 00:13:54,038
- Yu Bin is wavering.
- She's happy.

256
00:13:54,039 --> 00:13:57,549
Wasn't she basically a thing with Yoon Hoo?

257
00:13:57,679 --> 00:13:59,048
- That's wrong, Yu Bin.
- No.

258
00:13:59,049 --> 00:14:00,518
She's just checking the facts.

259
00:14:00,519 --> 00:14:02,378
- All you see isn't everything.
- It's not...

260
00:14:02,379 --> 00:14:04,248
What's the use of checking the facts?

261
00:14:04,249 --> 00:14:06,189
Yoon Hoo even went down on his knees earlier.

262
00:14:07,359 --> 00:14:08,559
Seriously.

263
00:14:09,119 --> 00:14:10,729
(Cheering)

264
00:14:15,659 --> 00:14:18,969
When I read the text and how it was written,

265
00:14:20,069 --> 00:14:22,999
I guessed it could be you.

266
00:14:23,169 --> 00:14:26,768
But I had a feeling you would've sent it to Si Woo.

267
00:14:26,769 --> 00:14:27,878
After all, you gave...

268
00:14:27,879 --> 00:14:29,079
- the flowers to her.
- Right.

269
00:14:31,849 --> 00:14:33,579
May I ask why you sent it to me?

270
00:14:36,349 --> 00:14:38,849
Why... Remember how I joined late?

271
00:14:39,419 --> 00:14:42,618
You asked if we'd like to play the board game together.

272
00:14:42,619 --> 00:14:45,388
That's what helped me start to loosen up a bit.

273
00:14:45,389 --> 00:14:47,499
I really appreciated that.

274
00:14:50,799 --> 00:14:51,999
She did.

275
00:14:52,569 --> 00:14:55,099
Can I also ask who you sent it to yesterday?

276
00:14:57,039 --> 00:15:01,509
Honestly, I was contemplating between you and Yoon Hoo.

277
00:15:01,639 --> 00:15:04,078
Since I got to know Yoon Hoo a bit more,

278
00:15:04,079 --> 00:15:05,549
I sent it to him.

279
00:15:07,049 --> 00:15:08,319
I see.

280
00:15:15,019 --> 00:15:18,929
You know how what you've written gets sent as is?

281
00:15:19,129 --> 00:15:22,258
I thought it was you based on it.

282
00:15:22,259 --> 00:15:24,129
- Really?
- Yes.

283
00:15:24,329 --> 00:15:27,068
- The text had this bright tone.
- Did it?

284
00:15:27,069 --> 00:15:29,769
I thought the bright tone of the text was from you,

285
00:15:30,639 --> 00:15:32,309
but it wasn't.

286
00:15:36,179 --> 00:15:37,949
"You were hungry, right? Was it good?"

287
00:15:39,679 --> 00:15:41,449
Should I say it was cute?

288
00:15:41,719 --> 00:15:44,589
The bright tone reminded me of Yu Bin.

289
00:15:45,919 --> 00:15:47,789
What did the text say?

290
00:15:48,359 --> 00:15:50,118
You can't tell me, can you?

291
00:15:50,119 --> 00:15:51,658
- That's a bit...
- Okay.

292
00:15:51,659 --> 00:15:53,829
But isn't it something you can tell me?

293
00:15:54,499 --> 00:15:58,029
It was asking if I enjoyed the meal.

294
00:16:00,299 --> 00:16:01,439
I see.

295
00:16:02,499 --> 00:16:03,839
To even ask about the content?

296
00:16:04,109 --> 00:16:05,968
- Even the content?
- Yu Bin...

297
00:16:05,969 --> 00:16:09,039
- Yu Bin, that's crossing the line.
- Calm down, Yu Bin.

298
00:16:09,509 --> 00:16:11,048
Hee Dong thought...

299
00:16:11,049 --> 00:16:14,119
the text was from Yu Bin...

300
00:16:14,249 --> 00:16:16,578
- "What? Who was it then?" - but realized it wasn't.

301
00:16:16,579 --> 00:16:18,818
- "Who was it?" - He could guess...

302
00:16:18,819 --> 00:16:20,659
it was from Si Woo.

303
00:16:22,219 --> 00:16:26,559
(Meanwhile, who came to talk to Jae Seung?)

304
00:16:27,799 --> 00:16:29,428
- Ten minutes to chat.
- Right.

305
00:16:29,429 --> 00:16:31,589
(1-on-1 Rotation Chat, Lee Jae Seung and Cho Eun Byul)

306
00:16:31,769 --> 00:16:33,998
This is my first time sitting here.

307
00:16:33,999 --> 00:16:35,799
(Jae Seung finally gets to talk to Eun Byul.)

308
00:16:37,839 --> 00:16:39,868
- Nice to meet you.
- Nice to meet you too.

309
00:16:39,869 --> 00:16:41,609
It's our first... No, it's not.

310
00:16:44,579 --> 00:16:46,609
- Jae Seung, it's your chance.
- Exactly.

311
00:16:46,649 --> 00:16:48,418
Eun Byul must have no idea that...

312
00:16:48,419 --> 00:16:51,018
- Jae Seung is interested in her.
- No.

313
00:16:51,019 --> 00:16:53,118
- He should make a move right now.
- Totally.

314
00:16:53,119 --> 00:16:54,989
- Things look good at the moment.
- Yes.

315
00:16:59,229 --> 00:17:01,799
How was your date? What was most memorable?

316
00:17:02,999 --> 00:17:04,829
It was our conversation.

317
00:17:04,929 --> 00:17:07,229
- Did you two talk a lot?
- Yes.

318
00:17:07,569 --> 00:17:09,769
- We did without any breaks.
- Is that so?

319
00:17:11,909 --> 00:17:14,109
(Thinking)

320
00:17:14,579 --> 00:17:15,609
How do you feel?

321
00:17:17,039 --> 00:17:20,049
How do you feel now?

322
00:17:20,619 --> 00:17:21,619
Me?

323
00:17:22,879 --> 00:17:26,318
I've always been open-minded, so...

324
00:17:26,319 --> 00:17:28,889
- You want to get to know them.
- Yes.

325
00:17:29,219 --> 00:17:31,229
So, you're not set...

326
00:17:32,159 --> 00:17:33,758
- on just one person.
- No.

327
00:17:33,759 --> 00:17:34,799
Okay.

328
00:17:38,469 --> 00:17:40,369
I was pretty surprised after hearing from her.

329
00:17:41,499 --> 00:17:44,408
I could tell that she and Jae Hyuk...

330
00:17:44,409 --> 00:17:45,639
had gotten really close.

331
00:17:45,969 --> 00:17:48,609
But she told me that she's keeping an open mind.

332
00:17:49,339 --> 00:17:53,109
I thought that I might get a chance later.

333
00:17:54,849 --> 00:17:55,918
She's open-minded!

334
00:17:55,919 --> 00:17:57,888
- Come in while it's still open!
- Yes.

335
00:17:57,889 --> 00:17:59,548
- Come in while it's open.
- Yes, it's a chance.

336
00:17:59,549 --> 00:18:00,619
Indeed.

337
00:18:02,689 --> 00:18:04,689
How about you? Do you only have one?

338
00:18:06,589 --> 00:18:07,629
For me,

339
00:18:08,629 --> 00:18:10,459
after the date,

340
00:18:13,569 --> 00:18:16,768
I changed my mind.

341
00:18:16,769 --> 00:18:19,468
(I changed my mind.)

342
00:18:19,469 --> 00:18:20,469
Yes.

343
00:18:25,209 --> 00:18:27,378
- Tell her who you changed to!
- That's right.

344
00:18:27,379 --> 00:18:28,848
- Tell her more!
- Who is it?

345
00:18:28,849 --> 00:18:29,878
- Is it her or not?
- Tell her who.

346
00:18:29,879 --> 00:18:31,289
- Who did he change to?
- Let's go.

347
00:18:31,389 --> 00:18:32,749
Tell her more.

348
00:18:34,089 --> 00:18:36,718
So, are you willing to talk to others?

349
00:18:36,719 --> 00:18:38,189
Yes.

350
00:18:42,029 --> 00:18:45,429
Eun Byul probably didn't notice it,

351
00:18:45,829 --> 00:18:49,669
but I tried giving her a hint.

352
00:18:51,069 --> 00:18:52,668
(That was a hint?)

353
00:18:52,669 --> 00:18:55,039
Gosh, this is so sad.

354
00:18:55,179 --> 00:18:56,278
This is your chance!

355
00:18:56,279 --> 00:18:58,248
She won't know if he's saying no...

356
00:18:58,249 --> 00:18:59,508
- or if he wants her...
- Right.

357
00:18:59,509 --> 00:19:01,079
- to approach him.
- It's ambiguous.

358
00:19:01,149 --> 00:19:03,179
- He said he was into Si Woo.
- Yes.

359
00:19:03,419 --> 00:19:05,748
And now he's expressed that he's no longer into her.

360
00:19:05,749 --> 00:19:07,018
But he never told Eun Byul...

361
00:19:07,019 --> 00:19:08,358
- that he was into Si Woo.
- No.

362
00:19:08,359 --> 00:19:09,618
- But it sounds like it.
- Do you think...

363
00:19:09,619 --> 00:19:12,128
Eun Byul is only interested in Jae Seung?

364
00:19:12,129 --> 00:19:14,599
She also has a lot on her mind.

365
00:19:14,729 --> 00:19:16,199
(Frustrated)

366
00:19:17,199 --> 00:19:20,869
(Hoo's partner hasn't come yet.)

367
00:19:24,469 --> 00:19:25,909
I should get some water.

368
00:19:33,809 --> 00:19:35,379
Hello.

369
00:19:36,679 --> 00:19:37,789
Hi, Si Woo.

370
00:19:38,989 --> 00:19:40,718
- "Hi, Si Woo?" - "Hi, Si Woo?"

371
00:19:40,719 --> 00:19:42,219
He's waiting for Si Woo.

372
00:19:43,019 --> 00:19:44,389
- "Hi, Si Woo." - Yes.

373
00:19:52,199 --> 00:19:53,829
It's about time she got here.

374
00:19:58,909 --> 00:19:59,938
- Hi.
- Here she comes.

375
00:19:59,939 --> 00:20:00,939
Who will it be?

376
00:20:01,779 --> 00:20:03,079
- Hello.
- Hello.

377
00:20:04,849 --> 00:20:05,849
(1-on-1 Rotation Chat, Yoon Hoo and Woo Seo Yoon)

378
00:20:05,850 --> 00:20:08,178
- My goodness.
- Seo Yoon came first!

379
00:20:08,179 --> 00:20:10,679
(1-on-1 Rotation Chat, Yoon Hoo and Woo Seo Yoon)

380
00:20:11,289 --> 00:20:12,689
- Nice to meet you.
- Yes.

381
00:20:13,619 --> 00:20:15,619
I got you a cup of water. It's yours.

382
00:20:19,889 --> 00:20:22,199
(Nervous)

383
00:20:22,959 --> 00:20:24,668
- Aren't you cold?
- No, I'm fine.

384
00:20:24,669 --> 00:20:25,799
Isn't it cold over there?

385
00:20:26,669 --> 00:20:28,098
- It's cold, but I'm fine.
- Right?

386
00:20:28,099 --> 00:20:29,139
Or...

387
00:20:29,239 --> 00:20:31,168
- No, it's fine.
- Do you want to put this on?

388
00:20:31,169 --> 00:20:32,239
Okay.

389
00:20:33,709 --> 00:20:34,709
Thank you.

390
00:20:34,710 --> 00:20:36,609
It's pretty windy over there.

391
00:20:37,079 --> 00:20:38,609
- It really is.
- Right?

392
00:20:40,509 --> 00:20:41,718
- Didn't he give that jacket...
- How could he...

393
00:20:41,719 --> 00:20:44,248
- He gave it to Yu Bin earlier.
- Hey!

394
00:20:44,249 --> 00:20:45,648
- Hey!
- Hey!

395
00:20:45,649 --> 00:20:46,788
- Hoo.
- We all saw it.

396
00:20:46,789 --> 00:20:48,118
You're giving it out to everyone.

397
00:20:48,119 --> 00:20:49,959
I told him to give the jacket...

398
00:20:50,059 --> 00:20:51,688
to anyone feeling cold.

399
00:20:51,689 --> 00:20:52,988
Did you?

400
00:20:52,989 --> 00:20:54,528
That jacket was for everyone.

401
00:20:54,529 --> 00:20:55,558
Okay.

402
00:20:55,559 --> 00:20:57,279
(The leather jacket is for all their kids.)

403
00:21:04,099 --> 00:21:06,209
Hoo seems really tense, though.

404
00:21:09,439 --> 00:21:10,849
How was your day?

405
00:21:12,249 --> 00:21:14,319
I'd say it was pretty fun.

406
00:21:15,019 --> 00:21:16,149
- I see.
- Yes.

407
00:21:17,249 --> 00:21:18,419
- "I see?" - Yes.

408
00:21:19,389 --> 00:21:20,959
Did you enjoy today's dinner?

409
00:21:21,059 --> 00:21:22,059
It was so tasty.

410
00:21:22,259 --> 00:21:24,019
Have you always been a good cook?

411
00:21:24,629 --> 00:21:26,559
- I've only grilled meat often.
- Just meat.

412
00:21:26,789 --> 00:21:28,198
Ramyeon and...

413
00:21:28,199 --> 00:21:30,399
Well, I can cook anything as long as I have the recipe.

414
00:21:30,799 --> 00:21:33,080
- So, you're good at grilling meat.
- Yes, grilling meat.

415
00:21:33,299 --> 00:21:34,438
Do you like meat?

416
00:21:34,439 --> 00:21:35,939
It's my favorite.

417
00:21:37,769 --> 00:21:39,069
- We have pork belly.
- Really?

418
00:21:39,539 --> 00:21:41,579
Have you heard of "crispy outside, juicy inside?"

419
00:21:42,939 --> 00:21:44,109
On high heat,

420
00:21:45,109 --> 00:21:47,848
you can cook it with some kimchi.

421
00:21:47,849 --> 00:21:48,849
(Thinking)

422
00:21:49,049 --> 00:21:51,019
Do you really like your steak well done?

423
00:21:51,249 --> 00:21:52,318
- No, right?
- Yes.

424
00:21:52,319 --> 00:21:54,118
They might spend ten minutes talking about food.

425
00:21:54,119 --> 00:21:55,819
I also like my steak that way.

426
00:21:55,989 --> 00:21:56,989
Really?

427
00:21:56,990 --> 00:21:59,228
Rather than medium rare...

428
00:21:59,229 --> 00:22:00,259
Yes.

429
00:22:02,029 --> 00:22:04,228
- Who cooks pork belly medium rare?
- This is a crucial moment, though.

430
00:22:04,229 --> 00:22:06,329
Does anyone cook pork belly medium rare?

431
00:22:07,299 --> 00:22:09,898
(Hoo told her all about how he likes his meat...)

432
00:22:09,899 --> 00:22:12,269
(as it's awkward.)

433
00:22:15,579 --> 00:22:18,178
It wasn't enough time...

434
00:22:18,179 --> 00:22:21,019
to develop an interest in him.

435
00:22:21,179 --> 00:22:24,849
I just learned that we were on the same wavelength.

436
00:22:28,959 --> 00:22:30,289
What else should I ask?

437
00:22:32,329 --> 00:22:34,729
(The chat has ended. Please head to the next location.)

438
00:22:35,029 --> 00:22:36,959
- I'll get going.
- Okay.

439
00:22:37,359 --> 00:22:38,529
- Thank you.
- Sure.

440
00:22:38,629 --> 00:22:39,899
- Have a good chat.
- Okay.

441
00:22:41,499 --> 00:22:43,638
She said, "Have a good chat," and left.

442
00:22:43,639 --> 00:22:44,738
- Seo Yoon...
- "Have a good chat."

443
00:22:44,739 --> 00:22:47,138
- She just left.
- She left in a hurry.

444
00:22:47,139 --> 00:22:49,979
(They only learned about their meat preference.)

445
00:22:51,149 --> 00:22:55,279
(After Yu Bin left, Hee Dong waits for the next person.)

446
00:22:56,179 --> 00:22:57,989
- Hello.
- Hello.

447
00:22:58,619 --> 00:23:02,088
(1-on-1 Rotation Chat, You Hee Dong...)

448
00:23:02,089 --> 00:23:04,488
(and Park Si Woo)

449
00:23:04,489 --> 00:23:06,459
- Hi.
- Hi.

450
00:23:07,959 --> 00:23:12,929
(Si Woo finally met Hee Dong.)

451
00:23:13,099 --> 00:23:15,268
- Si Woo is here!
- Si Woo!

452
00:23:15,269 --> 00:23:16,539
They finally meet.

453
00:23:17,299 --> 00:23:18,968
- I wonder what they'll talk about.
- Sir,

454
00:23:18,969 --> 00:23:20,449
- Si Woo is here.
- They finally met.

455
00:23:20,769 --> 00:23:22,039
She has a lot to say.

456
00:23:23,979 --> 00:23:26,308
He still hasn't read the letter from her, right?

457
00:23:26,309 --> 00:23:27,309
Not yet.

458
00:23:27,949 --> 00:23:30,618
- Express your feelings.
- You only get ten minutes.

459
00:23:30,619 --> 00:23:32,979
(It's a great chance to learn about each other's feelings.)

460
00:23:35,189 --> 00:23:36,619
I don't think we've ever talked...

461
00:23:37,159 --> 00:23:39,789
- Right? In private, I mean.
- before.

462
00:23:40,959 --> 00:23:42,059
Yes.

463
00:23:43,299 --> 00:23:44,328
(Shy)

464
00:23:44,329 --> 00:23:45,469
She's so happy.

465
00:23:45,799 --> 00:23:47,429
She's shy.

466
00:23:48,339 --> 00:23:50,039
How does it feel being here?

467
00:23:50,399 --> 00:23:51,469
Above all,

468
00:23:52,069 --> 00:23:53,969
it feels new.

469
00:23:54,479 --> 00:23:56,208
I got here late, right?

470
00:23:56,209 --> 00:23:59,049
So, I was more nervous.

471
00:24:01,419 --> 00:24:02,419
I see.

472
00:24:06,519 --> 00:24:07,589
You know,

473
00:24:09,119 --> 00:24:10,159
last night...

474
00:24:14,329 --> 00:24:15,798
You came...

475
00:24:15,799 --> 00:24:19,769
and gave me flowers, so I wanted to thank you.

476
00:24:23,639 --> 00:24:24,668
And...

477
00:24:24,669 --> 00:24:28,339
(She can't stop smiling.)

478
00:24:29,879 --> 00:24:32,678
I put it by the window...

479
00:24:32,679 --> 00:24:33,949
in case it withers.

480
00:24:35,849 --> 00:24:38,288
(She put Hee Dong's gift...)

481
00:24:38,289 --> 00:24:42,059
(on the windowsill next to her bed.)

482
00:24:44,689 --> 00:24:45,859
Please keep them fresh.

483
00:24:46,329 --> 00:24:47,329
I will.

484
00:24:48,229 --> 00:24:49,959
- I'll keep an eye on them.
- Good.

485
00:24:58,069 --> 00:24:59,968
(Shy)

486
00:24:59,969 --> 00:25:01,079
You know...

487
00:25:02,609 --> 00:25:06,008
Si Woo is really shy.

488
00:25:06,009 --> 00:25:07,108
- Is she always like that?
- Is she?

489
00:25:07,109 --> 00:25:09,248
- She's usually a sharp kid.
- Right.

490
00:25:09,249 --> 00:25:11,689
From the looks of it, she seems shy,

491
00:25:12,149 --> 00:25:13,889
but she also seems happy.

492
00:25:14,559 --> 00:25:17,989
It's nice to see her with a bright smile.

493
00:25:19,029 --> 00:25:21,028
Tell him about the letter, Si Woo.

494
00:25:21,029 --> 00:25:22,128
Yes, tell him.

495
00:25:22,129 --> 00:25:24,199
Ask him if he read the letter, Si Woo.

496
00:25:32,069 --> 00:25:33,109
Well...

497
00:25:35,279 --> 00:25:38,548
By the way, have you been here before?

498
00:25:38,549 --> 00:25:41,009
After we introduced ourselves.

499
00:25:42,619 --> 00:25:43,878
She's asking him now.

500
00:25:43,879 --> 00:25:45,288
- There you go.
- Good girl.

501
00:25:45,289 --> 00:25:46,388
(Will she bring up the letter?)

502
00:25:46,389 --> 00:25:48,659
- She'll talk about the letter now.
- She will.

503
00:25:49,310 --> 00:25:51,809
By the way, have you been here before?

504
00:25:51,810 --> 00:25:54,240
After we introduced ourselves.

505
00:25:54,880 --> 00:25:57,150
I was alone after everyone left,

506
00:25:57,580 --> 00:26:00,380
so I visited while looking around the 2nd and 3rd floors.

507
00:26:00,880 --> 00:26:02,250
(I see.)

508
00:26:03,190 --> 00:26:04,190
But...

509
00:26:04,990 --> 00:26:08,790
I realized that you could open it with the key.

510
00:26:10,060 --> 00:26:11,259
But you couldn't?

511
00:26:11,260 --> 00:26:13,399
No, I didn't know the keys were here.

512
00:26:13,400 --> 00:26:14,430
So,

513
00:26:14,970 --> 00:26:16,410
- you never got to open yours?
- No.

514
00:26:16,500 --> 00:26:19,039
- You haven't opened it yet?
- Not yet.

515
00:26:19,040 --> 00:26:20,040
Really?

516
00:26:20,570 --> 00:26:21,610
I see.

517
00:26:22,810 --> 00:26:27,680
(She found out that Hee Dong hasn't read her letter yet.)

518
00:26:30,080 --> 00:26:32,120
Why don't you open it now?

519
00:26:34,580 --> 00:26:36,350
Why don't you open it now?

520
