- It's perfectly fine to talk.
- I know...

1286
01:06:20,000 --> 01:06:21,569
that it's nothing serious.

1287
01:06:21,570 --> 01:06:23,239
- He understands.
- I understand.

1288
01:06:23,240 --> 01:06:24,769
You never know what will happen...

1289
01:06:24,770 --> 01:06:26,410
- because of that letter.
- That's right.

1290
01:06:26,440 --> 01:06:28,309
On the other hand, I'm proud of Hoo.

1291
01:06:28,310 --> 01:06:30,009
He gave Yu Bin closure...

1292
01:06:30,010 --> 01:06:33,080
by telling her that he enjoyed the day...

1293
01:06:33,480 --> 01:06:35,780
before writing a letter to Si Woo.

1294
01:06:36,120 --> 01:06:38,820
He's someone with clear boundaries.

1295
01:06:41,990 --> 01:06:43,630
They're still getting to know each other.

1296
01:06:45,090 --> 01:06:49,360
(Hoo sends letters to two people.)

1297
01:06:53,670 --> 01:06:55,140
It doesn't matter.

1298
01:06:55,470 --> 01:06:56,540
Just put it in there.

1299
01:07:05,910 --> 01:07:08,119
(A letter to Yu Bin)

1300
01:07:08,120 --> 01:07:12,950
(A letter to Si Woo)

1301
01:07:13,790 --> 01:07:17,230
(Hoo sent letters to two people.)

1302
01:07:18,590 --> 01:07:22,430
(The day ends with the swaying heart)

1303
01:07:28,740 --> 01:07:32,310
(The morning of the third day)

1304
01:07:32,940 --> 01:07:35,980
(Yu Bin and Seo Yoon's room, 8am)

1305
01:07:36,780 --> 01:07:41,220
(The daughters get ready diligently today as well.)

1306
01:07:41,650 --> 01:07:45,320
(Eun Byul and Si Woo's room, 8:10am)

1307
01:07:45,650 --> 01:07:47,820
What? It's snowing a lot.

1308
01:07:48,120 --> 01:07:49,260
My goodness.

1309
01:07:51,290 --> 01:07:54,299
It's pretty when it snows.

1310
01:07:54,300 --> 01:07:55,300
Right?

1311
01:07:59,830 --> 01:08:03,000
(They feel like a romantic day will begin.)

1312
01:08:07,610 --> 01:08:09,140
It's so pretty.

1313
01:08:09,680 --> 01:08:10,710
I know.

1314
01:08:11,410 --> 01:08:13,350
I hope this moment...

1315
01:08:14,520 --> 01:08:15,849
will continue on.

1316
01:08:15,850 --> 01:08:17,250
(May the happy moment continue on.)

1317
01:08:17,290 --> 01:08:19,390
Eun Byul seems to be very happy.

1318
01:08:21,460 --> 01:08:25,190
(1st floor kitchen)

1319
01:08:25,760 --> 01:08:30,160
(Seo Yoon comes out first and does the dishes.)

1320
01:08:31,700 --> 01:08:33,670
Eun Byul doesn't do the dishes anymore.

1321
01:08:34,270 --> 01:08:36,840
Min Soo pointed out something important.

1322
01:08:37,140 --> 01:08:41,080
Yes. Eun Byul doesn't come out to do the dishes anymore.

1323
01:08:42,810 --> 01:08:45,310
- You're right!
- It was a sharp comment.

1324
01:08:45,980 --> 01:08:48,049
(Day 1, before dinner)

1325
01:08:48,050 --> 01:08:50,549
(Day 2, before breakfast)

1326
01:08:50,550 --> 01:08:53,390
(Day 2, before the date)

1327
01:08:53,860 --> 01:08:57,230
(Eun Byul often did the dishes by herself.)

1328
01:08:57,960 --> 01:09:01,360
(Today, Seo Yoon is in the kitchen.)

1329
01:09:01,530 --> 01:09:04,099
Seo Yoon came out early to build connections.

1330
01:09:04,100 --> 01:09:05,269
The ones who are pressed come out to the kitchen.

1331
01:09:05,270 --> 01:09:06,329
You're right.

1332
01:09:06,330 --> 01:09:08,169
- You're right. They do that.
- Yes. The pressed one came out.

1333
01:09:08,170 --> 01:09:09,799
Seo Yoon came out first.

1334
01:09:09,800 --> 01:09:11,870
(Seo Yoon came out to the kitchen before anyone.)

1335
01:09:12,710 --> 01:09:13,740
Aren't you going to eat?

1336
01:09:14,980 --> 01:09:16,010
Do you want some?

1337
01:09:16,710 --> 01:09:17,780
- Do you want some?
- Yes.

1338
01:09:19,680 --> 01:09:20,680
Three?

1339
01:09:21,050 --> 01:09:22,380
Three, please.

1340
01:09:22,450 --> 01:09:25,650
Yu Bin is still in charge of food.

1341
01:09:25,820 --> 01:09:27,020
- Hello.
- Good morning.

1342
01:09:27,220 --> 01:09:28,889
- Good morning.
- Are you going to eat breakfast?

1343
01:09:28,890 --> 01:09:31,529
I'll eat with Eun Byul.

1344
01:09:31,530 --> 01:09:33,629
- I see. Okay.
- We promised to eat something else.

1345
01:09:33,630 --> 01:09:34,660
Okay.

1346
01:09:34,830 --> 01:09:37,060
(Smiling)

1347
01:09:40,000 --> 01:09:42,239
- Gosh, Shin Jae Hyuk.
- That's it.

1348
01:09:42,240 --> 01:09:43,910
They're no joke now.

1349
01:09:43,970 --> 01:09:45,710
They voice their interests outright.

1350
01:09:46,310 --> 01:09:48,080
- Gosh.
- They're smiling too.

1351
01:09:49,010 --> 01:09:50,690
Will you be able to ride them by yourself?

1352
01:09:50,950 --> 01:09:52,110
Shall we make a bet?

1353
01:09:52,480 --> 01:09:54,620
I'll make 3 rounds while you make 1 round.

1354
01:09:55,220 --> 01:09:57,950
(The loser will make breakfast tomorrow.)

1355
01:09:58,790 --> 01:10:01,296
(Eun Byul won, so Jae Hyuk got the penalty of making breakfast.)

1356
01:10:01,320 --> 01:10:03,659
- Did you pretend to be bad at it?
- No.

1357
01:10:03,660 --> 01:10:05,380
- How did you get better at it?
- I didn't.

1358
01:10:05,990 --> 01:10:09,400
So he keeps his promise.

1359
01:10:10,030 --> 01:10:14,370
(Jae Hyuk makes breakfast.)

1360
01:10:15,240 --> 01:10:18,210
(The breakfast is Jae Hyuk's cheese toast.)

1361
01:10:18,670 --> 01:10:19,670
Eun Byul.

1362
01:10:20,370 --> 01:10:21,440
It's ready.

1363
01:10:25,450 --> 01:10:29,250
(Full of ketchup)

1364
01:10:31,290 --> 01:10:34,920
(Like Jae Hyuk, Eun Byul tops it with a lot of ketchup.)

1365
01:10:35,390 --> 01:10:37,489
(The glutton, Hoo stands by their side.)

1366
01:10:37,490 --> 01:10:41,129
Hold on. Hoo is going, "Can I eat it?"

1367
01:10:41,130 --> 01:10:42,236
No one is making him breakfast.

1368
01:10:42,260 --> 01:10:43,300
Would you like to try it?

1369
01:10:45,130 --> 01:10:47,100
Try mine.

1370
01:10:47,340 --> 01:10:48,670
There's too much for me.

1371
01:10:49,040 --> 01:10:50,300
- Go ahead.
- All right.

1372
01:10:51,310 --> 01:10:53,979
(Thanks to Eun Byul, Hoo tastes the toast.)

1373
01:10:53,980 --> 01:10:55,610
Gosh, Jae Hyuk made it.

1374
01:10:55,840 --> 01:10:58,410
Hoo is eating the toast Jae Hyuk made.

1375
01:10:59,010 --> 01:11:01,180
- It's tasty.
- Really?

1376
01:11:02,880 --> 01:11:05,919
(She takes a photo of Jae Hyuk's toast.)

1377
01:11:05,920 --> 01:11:07,120
Thank you.

1378
01:11:09,490 --> 01:11:11,029
(Jae Hyuk's breakfast for Eun Byul)

1379
01:11:11,030 --> 01:11:13,490
(The part where Hoo took a bite)

1380
01:11:13,930 --> 01:11:17,870
(Eating)

1381
01:11:18,930 --> 01:11:21,270
(Eun Byul smiles happily.)

1382
01:11:22,770 --> 01:11:25,210
(Gazing)

1383
01:11:25,740 --> 01:11:29,040
(They begin the morning with their private breakfast.)

1384
01:11:29,310 --> 01:11:31,579
Gosh, it isn't like they're by themselves.

1385
01:11:31,580 --> 01:11:33,409
- They're having a sweet moment.
- Look at them.

1386
01:11:33,410 --> 01:11:35,180
(Satisfied)

1387
01:11:35,820 --> 01:11:38,720
(3rd floor Letter Room, at the same time)

1388
01:11:39,050 --> 01:11:40,249
- The Letter Room.
- Is it Si Woo?

1389
01:11:40,250 --> 01:11:41,460
Yes. Si Woo came upstairs.

1390
01:11:42,120 --> 01:11:46,260
(Si Woo visits the Letter Room while others are eating.)

1391
01:11:55,840 --> 01:12:01,680
(Si Woo receives a letter for the first time.)

1392
01:12:08,280 --> 01:12:09,380
My heart fluttered a bit.

1393
01:12:12,050 --> 01:12:13,990
"It's only the second day,"

1394
01:12:14,490 --> 01:12:16,019
"but we haven't had a long conversation."

1395
01:12:16,020 --> 01:12:17,929
"We only joke around here and there."

1396
01:12:17,930 --> 01:12:19,289
(But we haven't had a long conversation.)

1397
01:12:19,290 --> 01:12:20,659
(We only joke around here and there.)

1398
01:12:20,660 --> 01:12:23,100
(I want to have a conversation with you and get to know you.)

1399
01:12:23,600 --> 01:12:28,040
(Hoo manned up and delivered his feelings through a letter.)

1400
01:12:30,540 --> 01:12:32,709
(Who do you think sent you the letter?)

1401
01:12:32,710 --> 01:12:34,840
It's an anonymous letter.

1402
01:12:36,080 --> 01:12:38,156
The person who hasn't had a long conversation with me...

1403
01:12:38,180 --> 01:12:42,579
but only jokes around here and there...

1404
01:12:42,580 --> 01:12:45,220
has to be Hee Dong.

1405
01:12:46,690 --> 01:12:48,689
- She misunderstood.
- Oh, no.

1406
01:12:48,690 --> 01:12:49,789
It's a big mistake.

1407
01:12:49,790 --> 01:12:51,929
She misunderstood the identity of the sender.

1408
01:12:51,930 --> 01:12:53,830
- Exactly.
- My goodness.

1409
01:12:54,130 --> 01:12:56,960
Hee Dong is the only one in her head.

1410
01:12:57,130 --> 01:12:58,669
It's an accident.

1411
01:12:58,670 --> 01:12:59,999
(She mistook Hoo's letter for Hee Dong's.)

1412
01:13:00,000 --> 01:13:02,640
Si Woo's entire attention is on Hee Dong.

1413
01:13:02,670 --> 01:13:05,570
(The person who wrote a letter to Si Woo...)

1414
01:13:06,510 --> 01:13:10,240
(focuses on his cheese toast.)

1415
01:13:10,710 --> 01:13:12,750
This isn't the time to eat a toast!

1416
01:13:14,320 --> 01:13:16,950
(Meanwhile, Eun Byul comes out to the living room.)

1417
01:13:17,420 --> 01:13:18,420
Aren't you hungry?

1418
01:13:19,250 --> 01:13:21,050
I'm beginning to get hungry little by little.

1419
01:13:26,560 --> 01:13:29,100
What? Eun Byul received a text.

1420
01:13:30,130 --> 01:13:31,499
- Eun Byul received something.
- Eun Byul.

1421
01:13:31,500 --> 01:13:32,530
(What is it?)

1422
01:13:33,500 --> 01:13:34,569
(Women, please come to the Letter Room right now.)

1423
01:13:34,570 --> 01:13:37,200
"Women, please come to the Letter Room right now."

1424
01:13:37,370 --> 01:13:39,139
"But keep it a secret from men."

1425
01:13:39,140 --> 01:13:40,410
Why the Letter Room?

1426
01:13:41,140 --> 01:13:45,810
(Only the daughters received the text.)

1427
01:13:46,950 --> 01:13:48,519
Shall we take photos?

1428
01:13:48,520 --> 01:13:49,980
- Sure.
- I love the idea.

1429
01:13:53,920 --> 01:13:56,420
- "Keep it a secret?" - Yes. It's a secret from men.

1430
01:13:57,290 --> 01:13:59,330
What will happen in there?

1431
01:14:01,160 --> 01:14:02,300
Something...

1432
01:14:05,800 --> 01:14:09,840
(There's a box on the desk.)

1433
01:14:11,140 --> 01:14:12,369
This is so sudden.

1434
01:14:12,370 --> 01:14:13,910
- I know.
- It's scary.

1435
01:14:15,410 --> 01:14:16,480
Shall we open it?

1436
01:14:16,580 --> 01:14:17,650
Open it.

1437
01:14:18,910 --> 01:14:20,480
Who wants to open it?

1438
01:14:20,650 --> 01:14:22,250
- Me.
- Okay.

1439
01:14:22,480 --> 01:14:24,120
- Go ahead.
- Shall I open it?

1440
01:14:26,390 --> 01:14:31,260
(What's inside the box?)

1441
01:14:33,730 --> 01:14:34,800
What?

1442
01:14:36,860 --> 01:14:38,570
- Fortune cookies.
- Fortune cookies.

1443
01:14:39,730 --> 01:14:42,669
When we opened the box in the Letter Room,

1444
01:14:42,670 --> 01:14:46,109
we found four fortune cookies with our names.

1445
01:14:46,110 --> 01:14:48,740
(4 fortune cookies)

1446
01:14:49,180 --> 01:14:50,740
"The 1st-come 1st-served Date."

1447
01:14:51,110 --> 01:14:55,120
"Today, a special date for women is ready."

1448
01:14:55,680 --> 01:14:58,350
"Please deliver the fortune cookie with your name..."

1449
01:14:58,950 --> 01:15:02,619
"to the man of your choice to ask him out on a date."

1450
01:15:02,620 --> 01:15:03,919
(Please deliver the fortune cookie with your name...)

1451
01:15:03,920 --> 01:15:05,266
(to the man of your choice to ask him out on a date.)

1452
01:15:05,290 --> 01:15:08,100
"The date will be chosen on 1st-come, 1st-served basis."

1453
01:15:08,300 --> 01:15:11,000
"If the desired date has already been matched,"

1454
01:15:11,230 --> 01:15:13,900
"you must ask someone else out."

1455
01:15:14,470 --> 01:15:16,299
- it's the women's turn.
- it's the women's turn.

1456
01:15:16,300 --> 01:15:17,539
The rules are the same.

1457
01:15:17,540 --> 01:15:19,110
- Do they need to run?
- Yes.

1458
01:15:19,310 --> 01:15:20,339
This is important.

1459
01:15:20,340 --> 01:15:21,379
(If there's someone they want, speed is the key.)

1460
01:15:21,380 --> 01:15:22,480
This is very important.

1461
01:15:24,480 --> 01:15:25,650
Is it 1st-come, 1st-served?

1462
01:15:25,980 --> 01:15:27,480
Only we got the difficult choice.

1463
01:15:27,580 --> 01:15:28,980
Can we go now?

1464
01:15:30,050 --> 01:15:31,089
Are we going now?

1465
01:15:31,090 --> 01:15:32,290
Here I go.

1466
01:15:33,120 --> 01:15:34,359
(Yu Bin goes down the stairs first.)

1467
01:15:34,360 --> 01:15:35,460
She's going fast.

1468
01:15:35,560 --> 01:15:37,629
- All right.
- She's running.

1469
01:15:37,630 --> 01:15:39,829
- Yu Bin, read the room!
- She's going already.

1470
01:15:39,830 --> 01:15:42,030
Yu Bin, don't go to Hoo! Hoo wants to talk...

1471
01:15:42,360 --> 01:15:44,570
to someone else.

1472
01:15:44,970 --> 01:15:46,369
Yu Bin, lock Hoo up.

1473
01:15:46,370 --> 01:15:48,200
She's going fast.

1474
01:15:51,110 --> 01:15:52,240
She's going fast.

1475
01:15:52,570 --> 01:15:54,040
- I know.
- I'm joking.

1476
01:15:54,710 --> 01:15:55,740
I'm joking.

1477
01:15:56,580 --> 01:15:59,080
(The daughters walk down in an order.)

1478
01:15:59,150 --> 01:16:03,050
I'll look bad if you guys walk down elegantly!

1479
01:16:04,180 --> 01:16:05,420
Hold on a second.

1480
01:16:06,450 --> 01:16:08,420
I haven't made up my mind yet.

1481
01:16:11,990 --> 01:16:14,930
(Yu Bin comes down first.)

1482
01:16:16,130 --> 01:16:18,370
(Opening)

1483
01:16:18,670 --> 01:16:19,699
Hee Dong.

1484
01:16:19,700 --> 01:16:22,600
(Hee Dong.)

1485
01:16:25,140 --> 01:16:26,870
The first-come first-served Date.

1486
01:16:27,440 --> 01:16:28,840
There's a 1st-come 1st-served Date?

1487
01:16:28,880 --> 01:16:30,039
(Yu Bin chose Hee Dong, not Yoon Hoo.)

1488
01:16:30,040 --> 01:16:31,279
Really? Thank you.

1489
01:16:31,280 --> 01:16:32,310
Here.

1490
01:16:33,210 --> 01:16:34,750
- So you're asking Hee Dong?
- Yes.

1491
01:16:36,380 --> 01:16:38,820
- What?
- Oh, my.

1492
01:16:39,250 --> 01:16:41,720
Is Yoon Hoo... Yoon Hoo isn't in there, right?

1493
01:16:43,160 --> 01:16:44,160
Hey.

1494
01:16:44,161 --> 01:16:45,390
- See that?
- What happened?

1495
01:16:45,690 --> 01:16:47,359
- Yoon Hoo isn't in there, right?
- No.

1496
01:16:47,360 --> 01:16:49,059
(Yu Bin's father is speechless.)

1497
01:16:49,060 --> 01:16:51,299
Hold on. What's going on?

1498
01:16:51,300 --> 01:16:53,600
Instead of Yoon Hoo, why did Yu Bin...

1499
01:16:54,270 --> 01:16:55,399
What's going on?

1500
01:16:55,400 --> 01:16:57,470
(What's going on?)

1501
01:16:57,770 --> 01:16:59,710
That's not Yoon Hoo's room.

1502
01:17:00,470 --> 01:17:01,510
Yu Bin...

1503
01:17:01,940 --> 01:17:03,440
She chose Hee Dong?

1504
01:17:04,110 --> 01:17:05,749
- Yu Bin?
- Yu Bin?

1505
01:17:05,750 --> 01:17:06,950
She went to Hee Dong's room...

1506
01:17:08,050 --> 01:17:09,080
Thank you.

1507
01:17:11,120 --> 01:17:13,490
Do you have anyone you want to go on a date with?

1508
01:17:14,220 --> 01:17:17,189
I think it's important...

1509
01:17:17,190 --> 01:17:19,529
to talk to everyone once.

1510
01:17:19,530 --> 01:17:21,060
Understanding each other...

1511
01:17:21,300 --> 01:17:23,300
and getting along is most important.

1512
01:17:23,660 --> 01:17:26,470
I think I've only talked to one person.

1513
01:17:27,030 --> 01:17:30,400
Starting tomorrow, I want to talk to other people.

1514
01:17:31,710 --> 01:17:34,240
See? Everyone is the same.

1515
01:17:34,710 --> 01:17:38,310
I think I feel most comfortable with Hoo.

1516
01:17:40,080 --> 01:17:43,220
But I can't only talk to Hoo here.

1517
01:17:45,620 --> 01:17:48,159
I thought I should take my chance...

1518
01:17:48,160 --> 01:17:52,430
to talk to other people here.

1519
01:17:54,760 --> 01:17:56,099
(She decides to go on a date with someone else.)

1520
01:17:56,100 --> 01:17:58,100
- Yu Bin has that idea too.
- Of course.

1521
01:17:58,500 --> 01:18:01,739
She felt ennui at the same time.

1522
01:18:01,740 --> 01:18:02,740
That's right.

1523
01:18:03,900 --> 01:18:06,709
- I thought these two were close.
- Right.

1524
01:18:06,710 --> 01:18:08,016
They don't even hesitate to express it.

1525
01:18:08,040 --> 01:18:09,539
"I want to meet someone else."

1526
01:18:09,540 --> 01:18:11,310
- Right.
- They even say that.

1527
01:18:11,680 --> 01:18:13,449
- They're different.
- The generation has changed.

1528
01:18:13,450 --> 01:18:14,480
They're different.

1529
01:18:14,750 --> 01:18:16,619
- Not only Yoon Hoo had that idea.
- No.

1530
01:18:16,620 --> 01:18:18,390
- They all have the same idea.
- Yes.

1531
01:18:19,450 --> 01:18:20,450
Thank you.

1532
01:18:20,451 --> 01:18:24,160
(Hee Dong got a date request from Yu Bin.)

1533
01:18:25,360 --> 01:18:27,690
- Is it women's turn?
- It looks like it.

1534
01:18:30,660 --> 01:18:35,040
It was unexpected when Yu Bin chose me.

1535
01:18:36,070 --> 01:18:38,270
She came to me right away in the morning.

1536
01:18:38,440 --> 01:18:39,640
I have to say I was surprised.

1537
01:18:41,210 --> 01:18:42,709
If anyone was going to ask me out,

1538
01:18:42,710 --> 01:18:46,280
I wanted it to be Si Woo.

